209#define SENDMESSAGE(function_name,p) \
210auto ec = atp_trade_api_client->function_name(p); \
211if (ec != kSuccess) \
212{ \
213 std::cout << "send Error" << ec << std::endl; \
214 /*std::this_thread::sleep_for(std::chrono::seconds(5)); \*/\
215}

217template<size_t N>
218void SET(char (&a)[N],const std::string& str)
219{
220 strncpy(a, str.c_str(), N);
221}
222
223template<typename T1,typename T2>
224void SET(T1& t1,const T2& t2)
225{
226 static_assert(std::is_same<T1, T2>::value, "Types should be compatible");
227 t1 = t2;
228}
229
233uint64_t GenerateClientSeqID()
234{
235 //std::chrono::system_clock::time_point now = std::chrono::system_clock::now();
236 //std::chrono::time_point< std::chrono::system_clock, std::chrono::nanoseconds> ns =
237 // std::chrono::time_point_cast<std::chrono::nanoseconds>(now);
238 //return ns.time_since_epoch().count();
239 static uint64_t i=0;
240 return ++i;
241}
242
249//将收到的消息发送至ATPTradeAPI进行处理
250
251void SendCashOrder()
252{
253 ATPClientSeqIDType seq_id = GenerateClientSeqID();
254 ATPReqCashAuctionOrderMsg* p = new ATPReqCashAuctionOrderMsg;
255
256 strncpy(p->security_id, security_id.c_str(),9);
257 p->market_id = market_id;
258 strncpy(p->cust_id,cust_id.c_str(),17);
259 strncpy(p->fund_account_id, fund_account_id.c_str(),17);
260 strncpy(p->account_id, account_id.c_str(),13);
261 p->side = side;
262 p->order_type = order_type;
263 p->price = price;
264 p->order_qty = order_qty;
265 p->client_seq_id = seq_id;
266 p->order_way = order_way;
267 strncpy(p->user_info, user.c_str(),17);
268 strncpy(p->password, password.c_str(),129);
269 p->enforce_flag = enforce_flag;
270 p->stop_px = stop_px;
271 p->min_qty = min_qty;
272 p->max_price_levels = max_price_levels;
273 p->time_in_force = time_in_force;
274
275 std::cout << "send seq_id of order : " << seq_id << std::endl;
276
277 seq_cash_auction_map[seq_id] = p;
278
279 SENDMESSAGE(ReqCashAuctionOrder,p);
280
281}
282
283void SendCreditOrder()
284{
285 ATPClientSeqIDType seq_id = GenerateClientSeqID();
286 ATPReqCreditOrderMsg* p = new ATPReqCreditOrderMsg;
287
288 strncpy(p->security_id, security_id.c_str(), 9);
289 p->market_id = market_id;
290 strncpy(p->cust_id, cust_id.c_str(), 17);
291 strncpy(p->fund_account_id, fund_account_id.c_str(), 17);
292 strncpy(p->account_id, account_id.c_str(), 13);
293 p->side = side;
294 p->order_type = order_type;
295 p->price = price;
296 p->order_qty = order_qty;
297 p->client_seq_id = seq_id;
298 p->order_way = order_way;
299 strncpy(p->user_info, user_info.c_str(), 17);
300 memset(p->password, 0x0, 129);
301 strncpy(p->password, password_msg.c_str(), 129);
302 p->enforce_flag = enforce_flag;
303 p->stop_px = stop_px;
304 p->min_qty = min_qty;
305 p->max_price_levels = max_price_levels;
306 p->time_in_force = time_in_force;
307
308 std::cout << "send seq_id of order : " << seq_id << std::endl;
309
310 seq_credit_map[seq_id] = p;
311
312 SENDMESSAGE(ReqCreditOrder,p);
313
314}

326 p->side = side;
327 p->order_qty = order_qty;
328 p->client_seq_id = seq_id;
329 p->order_way = order_way;
330 strncpy(p->user_info, user_info.c_str(), 17);
331 strncpy(p->password, password_msg.c_str(), 129);
332 p->enforce_flag = enforce_flag;
333 strncpy(p->dest_account_id, dest_account_id.c_str(), 13);

471void SendOptionQuoteOrder()
472{
473
474 ATPClientSeqIDType seq_id = GenerateClientSeqID();
475 ATPReqOptionQuoteOrderMsg* p = new ATPReqOptionQuoteOrderMsg;
476
477 strncpy(p->security_id, security_id.c_str(),9);
478 p->market_id = market_id;
479 strncpy(p->cust_id,cust_id.c_str(),17);
480 strncpy(p->fund_account_id, fund_account_id.c_str(),17);
481 strncpy(p->account_id, account_id.c_str(),13);
482 strncpy(p->account_sub_code,account_sub_code.c_str(),7);
483 p->client_seq_id = seq_id;
484 strncpy(p->user_info, user_info.c_str(),17);
485
486 strncpy(p->quote_req_id,quote_req_id.c_str(),11);
487 p->bid_price = price;
488 p->bid_order_qty = order_qty;
489 p->bid_position_effect = bid_position_effect;
490 p->offer_price = offer_price;
491 p->offer_order_qty = offer_order_qty;
492 p->offer_position_effect = offer_position_effect ;
493
494
495

929void SendOptionCombinationOrder()
930{
931
932 ATPClientSeqIDType seq_id = GenerateClientSeqID();
933 ATPReqOptionCombinationOrderMsg* p = new ATPReqOptionCombinationOrderMsg;
934
935 strncpy(p->security_id, security_id.c_str(),9);
936 strncpy(p->cust_id,cust_id.c_str(),17);
937 strncpy(p->fund_account_id, fund_account_id.c_str(),17);
938 strncpy(p->account_id, account_id.c_str(),13);
939 strncpy(p->account_sub_code,account_sub_code.c_str(),7);
940 p->side = side;
941 p->order_qty = order_qty;
942 p->client_seq_id = seq_id;
943 //p->order_way = order_way;
944 strncpy(p->user_info, user_info.c_str(),17);
945 //strncpy(p->password, password.c_str(),129);
946 //p->enforce_flag = enforce_flag;
947 p->market_id = market_id ;
948 p->side = side ;
949 strncpy(p->strategy_id,strategy_id.c_str(),9);
950 strncpy(p->secondary_order_id,secondary_order_id.c_str(),17);
951
952 APINoLegsOrderUnit unit1,unit2 ;
953 strncpy(unit1.leg_security_id,leg_security_id1.c_str(),9);
954 unit1.market_id = market_id ;
955 unit1.leg_side = leg_side1 ;
956 unit1.leg_covered_or_uncovered = ATPCoveredOrUncoveredConst::kUnCovered;
957 strncpy(unit2.leg_security_id,leg_security_id2.c_str(),9);
958 unit2.market_id = market_id ;
959 unit2.leg_side = leg_side2 ;
960 unit2.leg_covered_or_uncovered = ATPCoveredOrUncoveredConst::kUnCovered;
961
962 p->no_legs_array.push_back(unit1);
963 p->no_legs_array.push_back(unit2);
964
965 std::cout << "send seq_id of order : " << seq_id << std::endl;
966
967 seq_combination_map[seq_id] = p;
968
969 SENDMESSAGE(ReqOptionCombinationOrder,p);

1491 strncpy(api_account_unit.account_id, p2, 13);
1492 p->account_id_array.push_back(api_account_unit);
1493 p2 = strtok(NULL, split);
